version_description: Also includes a tab of the riff.
Includes all accurate chords and strumming patterns.
Includes all accurate chords and inversions as well as chord diagrams.
This is the original version from On the Sunday of Live (1991), at least as close as I got to this, playing it in D tuning with a capo at fret 4.
Also includes a tab of the riff.
Includes accurate chords for all parts.
